{
  "stem": "12053.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were sort of-- we also had then German-Jewish customers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, the division didn't go into business like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we had a lot of customers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then as the Hitler times got worse, the Nazis-- we used to have them come in sometimes in a German uniform around the back of the shop-- it had a back entrance-- and pick up their laundry and support us as well.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's-- not to home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, we had a proper shop, proper business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't have a big laundry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was sort of-- what happened was we accepted it, sorted it and that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then it was sent to a very big laundry for the actual washing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then it came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was dried and then through a hot mangle and ironed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had women ironing and finishing it off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then my father used to-- he had a little, a little van.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he used to deliver it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I used to deliver on my bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was a terror on my bike.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had a bike.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The first-- I had the first bicycle in the whole school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my parents weren't very popular because of that, because the children nagged, the other children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they all wanted bikes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And for, for about a whole year, I was the most popular girl in school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Because they all learned to ride on my little bike.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So as I got bigger, I helped in the business after school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, and business did quite well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were never rich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I always remember my parents working very hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you asked me about Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, that's what I wanted to tell you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The shop also had a little kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
